content: With the Sunset of the Nine Skies Drink equipped to your Gourds, each sip recovers 35% of maximum health. Additionally, each sip grants a considerable amount of Qi - which is a nice bonus on top of the basic healing.

The content is as follows:
With the Sunset of the Nine Skies Drink equipped to your Gourds, each sip recovers 35% of maximum health. Additionally, each sip grants a considerable amount of Qi - which is a nice bonus on top of the basic healing.
